headline: Is Target open on Thanksgiving 2025?
summary: Thanksgiving may be only the second-most-popular holiday of the year in the U.S. (top billing goes to Christmas, and Halloween takes third place, according to a 2024 YouGov survey), but it's a day when food and table setting are tied for most important part of the day. headline: Seasonal hiring offers little reprieve for labor market woes
summary: As layoff announcements make waves and the unemployment rate creeps up, the usual holiday hiring spree appears muted this year.
